{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-goanimes-api",
    "name": "GoAnimes",
    "description": "GoAnimes — admin API + URLs úteis do addon Stremio.\n\n**Variáveis:** `baseUrl`, `adminApiKey`, `rssSourceId`, `sampleRssUrl`\n\nSe **não** usares `GOANIMES_ADMIN_API_KEY`, no Postman abre a pasta **Admin**, edita **Authorization** → Type **No Auth** (ou apaga o Bearer).\n\nO pedido **Create RSS source** grava o `id` devolvido em `rssSourceId` para usar no **Delete**.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8080" },
    { "key": "adminApiKey", "value": "" },
    { "key": "rssSourceId", "value": "" },
    {
      "key": "sampleRssUrl",
      "value": "https://www.erai-raws.info/feed/?type=torrent&token=SEU_TOKEN_AQUI"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Public (Stremio / health)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Manifest (addon Stremio)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/manifest.json"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Catalog movie / goanimes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/catalog/movie/goanimes.json"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
          {
            "key": "token",
            "value": "{{adminApiKey}}",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "RSS sources",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Create RSS source",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                      "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                      "  if (j && j.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('rssSourceId', j.id);",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"url\": \"{{sampleRssUrl}}\",\n  \"label\": \"Erai\"\n}"
                },
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rss-sources"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "List RSS sources",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rss-sources"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Delete RSS source",
              "request": {
                "method": "DELETE",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rss-sources/{{rssSourceId}}"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Sync",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Rebuild (sync now)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rebuild"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Sync status",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sync-status"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
